window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>In a world that's labeled me a b*stard, revenge is my redemption.</b></p> <p>Humiliation is the sweetest revenge. If I want to see my father's reputation in tatters, then I have to take his most prized possession: his new wife.</p> <p>I've waited twenty-five years to make him pay for what he's done. I don't want to hurt Carrie, but she's collateral damage.</p> <p>This world has branded me a b*stard... And it's time for me to embrace it.</p> <p>As the line between right and wrong blurs, one thing is clear: I'm ready to embrace the darkness within. But at what cost?</p> <p><i>Dark romance author Cora Kent brings you a forbidden romance between a man seeking revenge and the unknowing woman married to his father. </i>Sweet Revenge <i>is Jackson and Carrie's story. This novel features dark themes, steamy scenes, and mature content.</i></p> <p><i>Each book in the Blackmore University series can be enjoyed as a standalone novel. The Blackmore University trilogy is complete.</i></p>"; 
